{"tid":541018,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC] Hyper Universe 免費中文亞洲服橫向MOBA","createTime":"2018-01-26T04:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T03:13:28.000Z","uid":25608,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b5377629f2057592489c6b96adee2fec4310a0","tid":541018,"uid":25608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8TQWQcr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8TQWQcr.jpg&h=e0adf0d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">HYPER UNIVERSE</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Steam:<br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/591530/Hyper_Universe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F591530%2FHyper_Universe%2F&d=6b8NNPeCEMRihft%2FqxBOAqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=aa165cac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/591530/Hyper_Universe/</a><br />\n</span><br />\n鐘意玩MOBA game? 鐘意玩橫向過關game? 成日玩黎玩去都係LOL同DOTA2有d悶? Hyper Universe就岩晒你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uBY3BIUMew8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuBY3BIUMew8&d=6b8NNPeCEMRihft%2FqxBOAqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=64ddbcea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uBY3BIUMew8</a><br />\nGame play<br />\n<br />\nHyper Universe係由韓國nexon發行既橫向MOBA作品, 係韓國推出左大約一年既時間, 2018年1月17日係steam正式推出, 遊戲包含美國, 歐洲同亞洲3個server, 語言方面亦built in左中文, 岩晒唔想睇英文既朋友, 而遊戲亦都係免費既, 玩家可以pay cash去買hero, skin等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5WefEbA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5WefEbA.jpg&h=262a14ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢叫得MOBA game都不外乎推線, 清怪, 配裝, 依隻game既概念雖然同普通MOBA一樣, 但係最特別既就係 - 佢係一隻橫向捲軸結合左MOBA既遊戲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rd4iNL9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRd4iNL9.jpg&h=8cc97ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係mini map可以睇到, 成個map係分為上下7層, player可以用梯, 彈弓, 透明地板向上/向下移動, 每一層既map都會有唔同既分佈, 例如最其中幾層會有neutral mobs, 另外既層數會有自己/對方既defense tower, player需要技巧地係地圖唔同既層數移動, 獲取對自己/隊友既buff, 最終目標同其他MOBA一樣, <span style=\"color: red;\">destroy the enemy's base</span><br />\n<br />\nHyper Universe同其他MOBA唔一樣既地方就係, 裝備配置係需要入game前決定的, 每個角色都有自己既unique gear, 再配合埋唔同既general gear, 唔同既玩家可以將角色配置成唔同既玩法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NyRPpyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNyRPpyf.jpg&h=39777b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前Hyper Universe有41個hyper (即係hero), 分為tank, bruiser, specialist, striker, support同assassin 6大類, 數量唔算太多, 不過都足夠配合出多種打法<br />\n<br />\n暫時隻game既playerbase唔算大, 都係維持係千令二千人左右, 係放工放學時間排都要等幾分鐘先搵到match, 所以如果大家有興趣既不仿組隊玩下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd466447ded372cf968f0e4e4489473ca2450c5b","tid":541018,"uid":25608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"十連冇難度! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6f287b2c37c0ace7e400a5ca0c8802bc2f08f4","tid":541018,"uid":129931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:03:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44d3372c1693535b204cd40dc5e2ba36efdb877b","tid":541018,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"叫做唔錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105b8ce290ad0c78d732f9fc89fd76c660fa9ee4","tid":541018,"uid":124471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:35:25.000Z","msg":"有性趣. 可唔可以用手制玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4797d49c7d36585fe0c21a437cd1b807f69d516","tid":541018,"uid":25608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"可以呀, 我見有d player話用手制先真係玩緊依隻game <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16823cb4a410c943d8ba776dd19cccfb36caee5","tid":541018,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"用SUP英仲未贏過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ff4aec39a72e7f7a4e56458e4cf37221e2ed00","tid":541018,"uid":25608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d16823cb4a410c943d8ba776dd19cccfb36caee5","tid":541018,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"用SUP英仲未贏過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:13:28.000Z","msg":"ASIA唔同朋友排的話成日都遇到troll, 用sup單排好難贏"}]}